    {
      "id": 39,
      "section": {
        "id": 36,
        "title": "Personality",
        "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865",
        "updated": null,
        "parts": null
      },
      "type": {
        "id": 1,
        "name": "Paragraph",
        "feHandlerIndex": "Paragraph"
      },
      "displayText": "Sentence from me about me:",
      "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
      "updated": null,
      "displayOrder": 2,
      "contents": [
        {
          "id": 84,
          "content": "Don't like to give orders prefer to ask favors.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 1
        },
        {
          "id": 85,
          "content": "love to improve everything, You are included.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 2
        },
        {
          "id": 86,
          "content": "Love results, hate processes. If there is a way to get results without process, I will definitely find it.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 3
        },
        {
          "id": 87,
          "content": "I'm a lion person (like a cat one but with a loud roar).",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 4
        },
        {
          "id": 88,
          "content": "Love standing my ground.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 5
        },
        {
          "id": 89,
          "content": "Like to move by small steps, don't like rushing.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 6
        },
        {
          "id": 90,
          "content": "Like to get maximum out of what I have, won't search for something new if I can use the existing one.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 7
        },
        {
          "id": 91,
          "content": "Hate spaghetti. Love SOLID, work LoD",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 8
        },
        {
          "id": 92,
          "content": "Hate to do everything by myself. We are who we are due to uniting, not because someone had big biceps.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 9
        },
        {
          "id": 93,
          "content": "Brains are a muscle. If you need them, you must train them.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 10
        },
        {
          "id": 94,
          "content": "Don't say 'Maris, I'm okay with it' if it's not true. I will eat you like an ice-cream (with taste).",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 11
        },
        {
          "id": 95,
          "content": "Love predictable risk, hate risks that are not calculated.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 12
        },
        {
          "id": 96,
          "content": "If I fall, I will jump right back. Anything that doesn't kill me makes me stronger.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 13
        },
        {
          "id": 97,
          "content": "Don't be scared that you will harm my feelings.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 14
        },
        {
          "id": 98,
          "content": "I'm a mirror — I throw back everything you throw at me (it will fly even if I won't be able to lift it).",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 15
        },
        {
          "id": 99,
          "content": "Try harder is good, but think smarter is better!",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 16
        },
        {
          "id": 100,
          "content": "If you ask me to do something in the middle of the night, it will be done. But I will expect that we’ll work to make sure it never happens again.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 17
        },
        {
          "id": 101,
          "content": "I believe that valuable things need time. If you make something fast, why do you expect it to live another day without a problem?",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 18
        },
        {
          "id": 102,
          "content": "If I can calculate mistake at the end, I won't do it — as the result is fully predictable.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 19
        },
        {
          "id": 103,
          "content": "Lazy bastard making the maximum out of doing nothing.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 20
        },
        {
          "id": 104,
          "content": "My ideas are unique. If you think they are not, then you just never discussed anything with me.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 21
        },
        {
          "id": 105,
          "content": "I respect all people, no matter their status, skills, or any other thing that seems important for most people.",
          "created": "2026-03-11T08:24:28.493865Z",
          "updated": null,
          "displayOrder": 22
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
